Notification of Operating Procedure Update

*	The following new or revised ISO Operating Procedures have been
implemented and are posted for reference on the ISO Website.

ISO Operating Procedure posted:  M-402 Ancillary Service Procurement
Procedure
Version: 3.2
Effective Date: 1/8/02
Procedure Purpose: This procedure sets forth the actions to be undertaken by
ISO Grid Resource Coordinators (GRC) and Real-Time (RT) operations personnel
to manage the procurement of Ancillary Services (A/S). 
Changes / Reasons: Modified procedure to reflect automatic update for Outage
Scheduler.

*	Please find them at
http://www1.caiso.com/thegrid/operations/opsdoc/index.html under the
appropriate Operating Procedure section heading.

